1. Switch up down
2. emergency handle

- normal operation (emergency handle retracted).
  : requires hyds
  : cannot retract on ground
  
  parts:
    uplock
    downlock
    door
    bogeys
    
    uplock downlock modelled as single lock -ve for downlock 0 for unlocked, 1 for uplocked
    
emerg operation.
: handle pulled. hyds & electrics cut
-->
